## PART II — DEFINITIONS

"Software" : The Calakan application source code, configuration files,
database migrations, Blade templates, JavaScript files, CSS,
documentation, and all associated files in this repository.

"Contributor" : Any individual or entity that has contributed code,
documentation, design, or other materials to this project.

"Distribution" : Any form of making the Software available to third parties,
including but not limited to copying, packaging, deploying
on servers, or incorporating into another product.

"Modification" : Any change to the Software, including additions, deletions,
adaptations, translations, or derivative works.

"School Data" : Student personal information, attendance records, prayer
check-in data, form submissions, and any other data processed
by the Software that originates from SMKN 1 Ciamis users.

