## PART III — SCOPE & INTENDED USE

This Software was originally developed for internal use at SMKN 1 Ciamis
for the purpose of digitizing the Ramadhan activity book (Buku Ramadhan)
program for the 2025/2026 academic year.

You MAY:

- Use this Software as the basis for a similar program at another school
  or institution, provided attribution is given.
- Fork and adapt this Software for educational, non-commercial purposes.
- Study the source code for learning purposes.
- Contribute bug fixes and improvements via pull request.

You MAY NOT:

- Sell this Software or any direct derivative as a commercial product
  without explicit written permission from the copyright holders.
- Remove or obscure the copyright notices from any copies.
- Use SMKN 1 Ciamis branding, logo, or name to imply endorsement of a
  derivative product without prior written consent.
- Access, export, or redistribute actual School Data (student records,
  personal information) from any deployed instance of this Software.

---

## PART IV — DATA PRIVACY & STUDENT DATA PROTECTION

This Software processes personal data of students including but not limited to:
names, student ID numbers (NISN), class assignments, gender, religion, prayer
records, and daily Ramadhan activity submissions.

All school administrators and parties deploying this Software are responsible
for:

1. Complying with applicable data protection laws in Indonesia, including
   UU No. 27 Tahun 2022 tentang Perlindungan Data Pribadi (Personal Data
   Protection Law).

2. Ensuring that student data is not shared with unauthorized third parties.

3. Implementing appropriate security measures for the deployed instance,
   including HTTPS, strong authentication, and regular backups.

4. Obtaining necessary consent from students and/or guardians for the
   collection of personal data where required by law.

5. Providing users with the ability to request access to, correction of,
   or deletion of their personal data as mandated by applicable law.

The authors and copyright holders accept NO liability for improper handling
of personal data by parties deploying this Software.

